data.description: Stately 5 bedroom 4 bath home situated on 8 acres. Property features stables, paddock, hay barn, carriage house w 2 car garage, 3 car garage attached to residence, brand new hardwood floors throughout downstairs, new tile in primary bath and shared bath, new paint downstairs, gorgeous cathedral windows & fireplaces in both living rooms & one up. Downstairs bedroom is perfect as a guest room or great place for expansion for a downstairs's owner suite. Recent appraisal attached.
